content.rendered:
Exterior Colour Jet Black Metallic
Interior Colour Interior with extensive leather / Race-Tex items in Black with contrasting colour GT Silver

Individual equipment

-Decorative ‘PORSCHE’ side logo in black
Porsche Exclusive Manufaktur
-6-speed GT sports manual transmission
-Brake Calipers painted in Black (high-
gloss) Porsche Exclusive Manufaktur
-Front axle lift system
-20-/21-inch 911 GT3 wheels
-Wheels painted in Satin Black Porsche
Exclusive Manufaktur
-LED main headlights in Black incl.
-Porsche Dynamic Light System (PDLS)
-Porsche Exclusive Manufaktur
-Automatically dimming interior and
exterior mirrors with integrated rain
sensor
-ParkAssist (rear) including reversing
camera
-Adaptive Sports seats Plus (18-Way,
electric)
-Seat heating & Storage Package
-Seat Belts in Silver Grey Porsche Exclusive Manufaktur
-Rev counter in White Porsche Exclusive
Manufaktur
-Steering wheel rim and gear selector in
smooth-finish black leather
-Interior Package painted in exterior colour Porsche Exclusive Manufaktur
-Sports Seat Plus backrests in leather with decorative inlay in leather Porsche Exclusive Manufaktur
